(94, 'Terms_Condition_Discription', '<h2 class=\"font-weight-bold pb-3\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 2rem; color: #212529; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; padding-bottom: 1rem !important;\">Terms &amp; Conditions for Websites</h2>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Because a Terms and Conditions agreement is the agreement where you inform the users of your website about the rules, terms and guidelines that they need to follow in order to use and access your website,&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">a Terms and Conditions agreement has become extremely important.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">While it\'s not required by any laws currently (but third-parties such as Facebook may require it), through a Terms and Conditions you can maintain your rights to exclude certain users that may abuse your website or do not follow the rules you set.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">If you don\'t have this agreement for your website yet, use the Generator to create it!</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; width: 777px; color: #212529; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #0051aa; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; outline: none;\" href=\"https://www.termsfeed.com/blog/sample-terms-and-conditions-template/#Download_Terms_And_Conditions_Template\">Our Terms and Conditions template</a>&nbsp;will get you started with creating your own custom Terms and Conditions agreement.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; width: 777px; color: #212529; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\">This Terms and Conditions template is free to download and use for your website or mobile app.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; width: 777px; color: #212529; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\">A&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">Terms and Conditions agreement</span>&nbsp;is the agreement that includes the terms, the rules and the guidelines of acceptable behavior and other useful sections to which users must agree in order to use or access your website and mobile app.</p>\r\n<div id=\"toc_container\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #212529; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\">\r\n<div id=\"toc\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; width: 777px; color: #555555; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.125); box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 3px 6px 0px; border-radius: 3px; padding: 20px 30px 10px; margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 5px;\">\r\n<div class=\"toc_list_container\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<ul class=\"toc_list\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; list-style: none;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 7px; position: relative; display: block; margin-top: 7px;\"><a class=\"space_h2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; outline: none; display: flex; font-weight: bold; padding-left: 0px;\" href=\"https://www.termsfeed.com/blog/sample-terms-and-conditions-template/#What_Are_Terms_And_Conditions\"><span class=\"toc_text_position\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">1.</span><span class=\"toc_text_title\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-left: 5px;\">What are Terms and Conditions</span></a></li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 7px; position: relative; display: block; margin-top: 7px;\"><a class=\"space_h3\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; outline: none; display: flex; padding-left: 25px;\" href=\"https://www.termsfeed.com/blog/sample-terms-and-conditions-template/#What_To_Include_In_A_Terms_And_Conditions\"><span class=\"toc_text_position\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">1.1.</span><span class=\"toc_text_title\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-left: 5px;\">What to include in a Terms and Conditions</span></a></li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 7px; position: relative; display: block; margin-top: 7px;\"><a class=\"space_h2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; outline: none; display: flex; font-weight: bold; padding-left: 0px;\" href=\"https://www.termsfeed.com/blog/sample-terms-and-conditions-template/#Faq_Terms_And_Conditions\"><span class=\"toc_text_position\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">2.</span><span class=\"toc_text_title\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-left: 5px;\">FAQ: Terms and Conditions</span></a></li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 7px; position: relative; display: block; margin-top: 7px;\"><a class=\"space_h3\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; outline: none; display: flex; padding-left: 25px;\" href=\"https://www.termsfeed.com/blog/sample-terms-and-conditions-template/#Is_A_Terms_And_Conditions_Required\"><span class=\"toc_text_position\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">2.1.</span><span class=\"toc_text_title\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-left: 5px;\">Is a Terms and Conditions required?</span></a></li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 7px; position: relative; display: block; margin-top: 7px;\"><a class=\"space_h3\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; outline: none; display: flex; padding-left: 25px;\" href=\"https://www.termsfeed.com/blog/sample-terms-and-conditions-template/#How_To_Enforce_Terms_And_Conditions\"><span class=\"toc_text_position\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">2.2.</span><span class=\"toc_text_title\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-left: 5px;\">How to enforce Terms and Conditions</span></a></li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 7px; position: relative; display: block; margin-top: 7px;\"><a class=\"space_h2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; outline: none; display: flex; font-weight: bold; padding-left: 0px;\" href=\"https://www.termsfeed.com/blog/sample-terms-and-conditions-template/#Examples_Of_Terms_And_Conditions\"><span class=\"toc_text_position\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">3.</span><span class=\"toc_text_title\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-left: 5px;\">Examples of Terms and Conditions</span></a></li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 7px; position: relative; display: block; margin-top: 7px;\"><a class=\"space_h2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #555555; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; outline: none; display: flex; font-weight: bold; padding-left: 0px;\" href=\"https://www.termsfeed.com/blog/sample-terms-and-conditions-template/#Download_Terms_And_Conditions_Template\"><span class=\"toc_text_position\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">4.</span><span class=\"toc_text_title\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-left: 5px;\">Download Terms and Conditions Template</span></a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h2 id=\"What_Are_Terms_And_Conditions\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 35px; margin-bottom: 30px; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 2rem; color: #212529; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">What are Terms and Conditions</h2>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; width: 777px; color: #212529; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\">Terms and Conditions agreements act as a legal contract between you (the company) who has the website or mobile app and the user who access your website and mobile app.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; width: 777px; color: #212529; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\">Terms and Conditions are also known as Terms of Service or Terms of Use.</p>'),
